query: SELECT j.id, j.keyword, j.status, r.facets FROM analysis_jobs j LEFT JOIN analysis_reports r ON j.id = r.jobId WHERE j.keyword LIKE '%ハリアー%' ORDER BY j.id DESC LIMIT 5;
